metadata.name: Beach of Obsolescence
metadata.description:
As the tide rolled in, the ancient monitor on the beach flickered to life. The image of a haunting woman trapped on the screen, surrounded by ancient ruins. As you approach, her screams pierce the air, a warning to stay away or join her in her eternal prison

This image was generated by entering descriptive command prompts into AI system Midjourney. This is a 1/1 image.
